{"tid":495792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賺大錢仲「共渡時艱」？加薪6%先啱！","createTime":"2017-12-11T05:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T05:47:54.000Z","uid":110876,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"79c9d50113607ce5804c6d9d6dc283858262ee75","tid":495792,"uid":110876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:00:04.000Z","msg":"職工盟指香港過去一年經濟暢旺，建議各企業明年加薪幅度應不低於6%，以回饋員工的貢獻。職工盟主席吳敏兒說，就業市場求過於供，但沒有因此帶動工資顯著上升，扣除物價變動後，今年第二季私營機構僱員平均薪金只按年增加1.7%，遠低於同期實質經濟增長3.9%。<br />\n<br />\n她指，僱員工資長期低於勞動生產力增長，2006至2015年間，兩者累積差距接近25個百分點。今年經濟按年實質增長率為3.7%，估計甲類消費物價指數將上升2.2%，因此2018年合理加薪幅度應至少有6%。她認為，僱主在經濟表現強勁及前景樂觀的情況下，沒有理由不為員工加薪，如僱主只講共渡時艱，不提分享成果，會打擊員工士氣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有咁嘅可能性嗎？ 6%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ed329feb2503a80cec0c73038b4dd25d8f9858","tid":495792,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:23:42.000Z","msg":"職工盟有無加自己員工6%先？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b6bfb88ecf10059d6936fe54f953ead4bee969","tid":495792,"uid":53575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:27:34.000Z","msg":"香港企業唔減人工算好喇"},{"pid":"38376b94396cc069ff9fa589b7a66db93d902e46","tid":495792,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:30:50.000Z","msg":"香港人以經睇加人工睇得好開架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5e7450c968006f0a1840a74a563ebe35bd1bba","tid":495792,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:33:11.000Z","msg":"比D老闆賺晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有錢從來唔到打工仔賺"},{"pid":"14ef96e4068a068ed05ccea0854782eebde85fe5","tid":495792,"uid":149070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited